surf_kalium made by Helix

Map has 4 stages

1 = very easy
2 = medium
3 = hard
4 = very hard

There is 1 bonus, can be accessed at the beginning of stage 1. Note that the teleporter between the first 2 ramps of bonus is not the end but just the escape teleporter. The end of bonus can be beaten by entering the trigger and WALK towards the end.

This map has been on my computer for 1.5 years, so in fact, yeah, it took  1.5 years to finish (also counting the many months I did nothing about it)

Finally it's here! Enjoy!
